{"tid":1844130,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[抵制TVB系列] 大家唔好比津路烏龍茶撚","createTime":"2020-01-26T13:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T12:56:48.000Z","uid":163499,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"75c55f340ada74c4a3277b30cd5262f03a660ef9","tid":1844130,"uid":163499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:29:10.000Z","msg":"話說津路喺CCTVB落咗個短短地嘅罐頭新年廣告<br />\n比人發現之後今日話搵agency<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟進</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z50UhPR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ50UhPR.png&h=7de845d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身為行內人 依據我嘅觀察<br />\n本身津路都好少拍廣告/ 喺任何media platform落廣告<br />\n但佢今次係要揀TVB落 (過咗7個月 唔好同我講佢in-house marketing team/ media agency都唔知咩叫<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">抵制CCTVB)</span></strong><br />\n到過埋2019都仲落即係同香港人過唔去<br />\n落完廣告依家話「跟進」 (扮撤回？)<br />\n我自己覺得有少少似呃光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見留言有人話撤回就幫佢入幾箱<br />\n唔該咪撚癲喇<br />\n佢到2020都仲會落CCTVB就一定要屌佢老母<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">佢識聽民意「撤回」嘅<br />\n可以唔狙擊 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但一定唔撚可以懲罰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n要follow up<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3658d4ac709e422aa60baca96813be30945b77","tid":1844130,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:34:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.29 抗疫三罷 我地一齊罷！ 齊上齊落<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844116</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ef47fe2dde4d857ce5fae287135a7858705f749a","tid":1844130,"uid":295532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:44:12.000Z","msg":"罷買零食藍商江戶、僑豐行：EDO、巨浪大切、Dessert Duet、アメ橫丁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1843489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1843489</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b09275b1d703d6e8928796d52c18a6fdbd3142cb","tid":1844130,"uid":314682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a234c8027f8071db9869c3aebcab6fa7d4c693","tid":1844130,"uid":163499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1756f48e801d8967b30a61cf6ca6ce8f5ef350ad","tid":1844130,"uid":163499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:31:06.000Z","msg":"仲有好多人飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1ee482679ce08189aac51d838e1c49e6aa6706","tid":1844130,"uid":86040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:35:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"06c64e9278fe4d0a6bbeb9cf4780af3ec2c9d0ff","tid":1844130,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:36:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bdbd67353bcb7d672a8197e0a25ae87735e8eaed","tid":1844130,"uid":11463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:45:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca6b7e681ae204a35736b94ff296dd205cc7d5c1","tid":1844130,"uid":177620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"咁飲咩好，道地都有落廣告"},{"pid":"0f4d1148e8b488a379954db3e9fddf3394191bd5","tid":1844130,"uid":125026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca6b7e681ae204a35736b94ff296dd205cc7d5c1","tid":1844130,"uid":177620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"咁飲咩好，道地都有落廣告"},"cit